# This git repository (origin: github.com/ahouchell-rgb/retrieval-app) is rooted
# at the home directory but only versions the retrieval-app project.
# Ignore everything else so stray home-directory files — ~/.env.local, shell
# history, SSH/git config, other projects — can never be accidentally staged
# or pushed to the retrieval-app remote.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/Downloads/
/Downloads/*
!/Downloads/retrieval-app/
